"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T01:09:17.000Z","msg":"有無news睇下"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T01:13:47.000Z","msg":"要上 twitter 同台灣個邊<br />\n<br />\n台灣生果兩日前更新：中國水災災情由12省擴大至22省，受災人數突破500萬人"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T01:15:16.000Z","msg":"老老實實呢啲水災算唔算每年都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T01:17:01.000Z","msg":"咁大範圍都唔常見<br />\n九一個次原來受災都差唔多<br />\n<br />\n1991年5、6月間，中國共有18個省、自治區、直轄市發生水災，5個省、自治區發生嚴重旱災。災害最重、損失最大的是遭到洪水侵襲的安徽省和江蘇省。據當時初步統計，安徽省受災人口達4800多萬人、佔全省總人口近70％，因災死亡267人，農作物受災面積430多萬公頃，各項直接經濟損失金額將近人民幣70億元。江蘇省受災人口達4200多萬人、佔全省總人口的62％，因災死亡164人，農作物受災面積300萬公頃，各項直接經濟損失金額人民幣90億元。無家可歸的災民200萬人在淮河大堤上搭起了一眼望不到頭的臨時帳棚。"},{"pid":"8a5c64994b8e30fb6a32e4e64dca8ef430081e90","tid":2064510,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T01:17:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2020-06-13/41314458\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2020-06-13%2F41314458&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8vFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=26170549\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2020-06-13/41314458</a><br />\n睇到無乜感覺"},{"pid":"d1ec22e78472a09a08f16f0fcbd7790a02f83cc3","tid":2064510,"uid":66202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T01:18:19.000Z","msg":"死光最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9d0491d3972f31bd0142a491556a9dfcca48e07","tid":2064510,"uid":230146,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"7640e343b29b487278c070e5fe10146857b44385","tid":2064510,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d02086b87ad5c6faf7029c445053720d94f06932","tid":2064510,"uid":20414,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"828419079b09f505134e0bced61b08a9116f84aa","tid":2064510,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T01:09:17.000Z","msg":"有無news睇下"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T01:13:47.